Adding Cisco Call to Microsoft Teams
To place or receive calls from Microsoft Teams using your UB phone number, we recommend installing the Cisco Call app within Teams.

Dental school students/UB student assistants with exception accounts: Use Jabber due to Cisco Call/Webex login problems
Dental school students and UB student assistants with exception accounts attempting to log into Cisco Call will experience the following sign-in error: “Use a different email address or contact your buffalo.edu admin to create an account.” 

These student employees should continue to use Jabber for phone services until further notice. 

